  "description": "Six layers at zero symmetry, fold point at 0.5, fold amount at 0.5 — the mathematical midpoint of all possible fold states. The layered folds create a harmonic fractal: each layer adds a self-similar but offset version of the previous. The filter is barely open. A sustained note sounds like the universe folding in on itself at 1 Hz.",
